DAT
id=qid::label=str::text=lstr::
6538::$$$message_0056_0000_0000$$$::Hello!!! I'm Taiga Fujimura, the instructor for Tiger Dojo, a segment of the game that sweeps your sorry dead ass back up and gets you back on your feet... The segment of everyone's dreams!::
6539::$$$message_0056_0000_0001$$$::Hi! I'm Illya, and there's really no need for me to even be here, but I'm doing it as a favor for Taiga.::
6540::$$$message_0056_0000_0002$$$::Dyaaahhh!!!::
6541::$$$message_0056_0000_0003$$$::Disciple Number One! Your name here in this dojo is Disciple Number One!::
6542::$$$message_0056_0000_0004$$$::Ouch... I can't believe you blew me away... That phantasmic tiger bamboo sword is something to be reckoned with...::
6543::$$$message_0056_0000_0005$$$::                    "Tiger bamboo sword" has been added to the weapons dictionary.::
6544::$$$message_0056_0000_0006$$$::Huh? Did you just hear a weird sound?::
6545::$$$message_0056_0000_0007$$$::I didn't hear anything. Anyway, Taiga, what's today's theme?::
6546::$$$message_0056_0000_0008$$$::Hm. We're going to talk about bad ends today.[lr]::
6547::$$$message_0056_0000_0009$$$::Let me get right to the point: Always keep in mind that in [font italic=true]Fate,[font italic=false] letting your guard down leads only to defeat.::
6548::$$$message_0056_0000_0010$$$::There is no mercy in this game, from anyone, so common sense says you should save before you make a choice. After all, Shirou's life is like an intersection full of red lights.::
6549::$$$message_0056_0000_0011$$$::Yeah. Big brother is so dense. I knew it. I need to protect him.::
6550::$$$message_0056_0000_0012$$$::Chesuto!!!::
6551::$$$message_0056_0000_0013$$$::Ouch! Mentor, that bamboo sword really hurts! Please use something gentler!::
6552::$$$message_0056_0000_0014$$$::Denied. A kiddo who kills out of love needs to run three laps around the dojo. Now get going!::
6553::$$$message_0056_0000_0015$$$::Whaaat? I hate doing things that wear me out!::
6554::$$$message_0056_0000_0016$$$::Don't you want a tiger stamp!?::
6555::$$$message_0056_0000_0017$$$::Sheesh. Fine. I'm going.::
6556::$$$message_0056_0000_0018$$$::Anyway. The cause of death this time was that you stupidly believed you could run away from that sinister kiddo. ::
6557::$$$message_0056_0000_0019$$$::When you meet her, you either defeat her or get defeated.[lr]::
6558::$$$message_0056_0000_0020$$$::Being half-assed about it will get you killed, so be careful.::
6559::$$$message_0056_0000_0021$$$::Tiger? There's a cat in the corner of the dojo.::
6560::$$$message_0056_0000_0022$$$::Step on its tail to drive it away.[lr]::
6561::$$$message_0056_0000_0023$$$::And don't call me Tiger.::
6562::$$$message_0056_0000_0024$$$::Okay. I drove the weird-looking cat away.::
6563::$$$message_0056_0000_0025$$$::Very good. Then that concludes our lesson for today.::
6564::$$$message_0056_0000_0026$$$::The story's just begun. Once you get through this exciting part, your battles as a Master will begin...or...not begin...er, maybe?::
6565::$$$message_0056_0000_0027$$$::Which is it?::
6566::$$$message_0056_0000_0028$$$::Hmmm, maybe the training segment continues...just a little bit more...?::

